Package: MorphoGAM
Type: Package
Title: Identify spatially variable genes by projecting to morphologically relevant curves
Version: 1.1.1
Author: Phillip B. Nicol <philnicol740@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Phillip B. Nicol <philnicol740@gmail.com>
Description: Includes methods (interactive and automatic) for estimating a "morphologically relevant" 
 curve from spatial transcriptomics data. Implements a generalized additive model (GAM) to identify
 gene expression variation along the curve. 
